Job Description: Software Development Engineer (SDE) 

Job Title: Software Development Engineer (SDE) 
Location: Remote 
Job Type: Full-time 

About the Role:We are seeking a Software Development Engineer (SDE) with a strong background in software development and problem-solving skills. You will design, develop, and maintain scalable software solutions. 
Responsibilities 
Design, develop, and maintain high-quality software. 
Collaborate with teams to define and ship new features. 
Write clean, scalable, and efficient code. 
Troubleshoot, debug, and optimize performance. 
Participate in code reviews and stay updated with industry trends. 
Requirements 
Education: Bachelor’s or Master’s in Computer Science or related field. 
Experience: 2+ years in software development. 
Programming: Proficiency in Python, Java, or C++. 
Web Development: Experience with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and frameworks like React or Angular. 
Databases: Knowledge of SQL and NoSQL (e.g., MySQL, MongoDB). 
Tools: Familiarity with Git, Docker, and CI/CD pipelines. 
Cloud Platforms: Experience with AWS, Azure, or Google Cloud. 
Skills: Strong problem-solving and communication skills. 
Preferred Qualifications 
Experience with microservices architecture. 
Knowledge of machine learning frameworks like TensorFlow or PyTorch. 
Familiarity with Agile methodologies.